scrollkeeper: scrollkeeper (Cataloging System for Documentation)
scrollkeeper:
scrollkeeper: ScrollKeeper is a cataloging system for documentation. It manages
scrollkeeper: documentation metadata as specified by the Open Source Metadata
scrollkeeper: Framework (OMF) and provides a simple API to allow help browsers to
scrollkeeper: find, sort, and search the document catalog. It will also be able to
scrollkeeper: communicate with catalog servers on the Net to search for documents
scrollkeeper: which are not on the local system.
scrollkeeper:
